	* window.c (decode_window, decode_any_window): Move up in code.
	(Fwindowp, Fwindow_live_p): Rewrite doc-strings.
	(inhibit_frame_unsplittable): Remove unused variable.
	(Fwindow_buffer): Move up and rewrite doc-string.
