	* syntax.h (SETUP_SYNTAX_TABLE_FOR_OBJECT): Fix setting of
	gl_state.e_property when gl_state.object is Qt.

	* insdel.c (make_gap_larger): Remove limitation of buffer size
	to <= INT_MAX.

